{"tid":882354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新流感藥一粒見效　勁過特敏福","createTime":"2018-10-30T05:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:25:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c7faa4cb16109462597f083575381eac5515fdea","tid":882354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181030/20534105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F20534105&d=%2BpoJmaSyVHiK8oM95kKNaf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=213eaae4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F20534105&h=4cc41f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181030/20534105</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月30日 <br />\n<br />\n新流感藥一粒見效　勁過特敏福<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181030/large/a0603a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181030%2Flarge%2Fa0603a.jpg&h=19a2babe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】臨近年尾，北半球地區又正在醞釀冬季流感。不過美國食品及藥物管理局（FDA）為醫學界帶來喜訊，核准由羅氏藥廠及日本塩野義製藥共同研發的抗流感藥物「Xofluza」應用於臨床治療，是約20年前批准流感藥特敏福（Tamiflu）後，首次再批准新流感藥物。<br />\n<br />\n與特敏福一樣，Xofluza的服用黃金時間為病徵出現後的48小時內；但新藥只需服1次即可紓緩病徵，較特敏福快。本港衞生署指，已於上周收到Xofluza的註冊申請，正在處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n並非流感疫苗替代品<br />\n<br />\nFDA上周發表公告指，根據廠方早前進行的臨床試驗，安排1,832名流感患者分別接受Xofluza、特敏福，或服用安慰劑（placebo），結果發現服Xofluza的患者，只需一粒即可紓緩流感症狀，較服安慰劑的一組快，亦毋須像特敏福般需每日服藥兩次並維持五日。<br />\n<br />\nFDA認為，雖少數人服Xofluza後出現腹瀉、支氣管炎等副作用，但藥物整體安全及有效，批准於臨床應用。<br />\n<br />\n當局認為，由於流感病毒有可能對藥物產生抗藥性，故增加治療選擇有助擊退每年的流感高峯。但當局提醒不論是特敏福或Xofluza，都只是壓抑症狀的藥物，並非流感疫苗的替代品，公眾仍應接種疫苗預防流感為上。<br />\n<br />\n本港衞生署表示，正處理Xofluza的註冊申請；一般而言，可於5個月內完成註冊審批。 <br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n按戶按袋每公升$0.11<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n黃偉綸：交椅洲填海變新中環"},{"pid":"43a313d65653d334f5e1d00f12466c805fb3e425","tid":882354,"uid":79993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"留名等睇被人濫用，令到病毒變到有抗藥性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a28463c4474d26a72ceb196385649c6a76d36e5","tid":882354,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"83824e8a09c75bd29a804b0bd4b264781998b629","tid":882354,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"姓羅嘅應該中國人黎<br />\n中國又威威了"},{"pid":"9089bd3c7ea859dea88cb190df941189819d9689","tid":882354,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"做福人民"},{"pid":"28fe12971a281cb0fadea3e588b0ee21ca52621b","tid":882354,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">只需一粒即可紓緩流感症狀，較服安慰劑的一組快 </span><br />\n<br />\n安慰劑有治療效果??"},{"pid":"1a5001fb8448dbe761f52971cac5e35545b190d5","tid":882354,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28fe12971a281cb0fadea3e588b0ee21ca52621b","tid":882354,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">只需一粒即可紓緩流感症狀，較服安慰劑的一組快 </span><br />\n<br />\n安慰劑有治療效果??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"流感又唔係絕症，唔食藥都會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61f5bef756e957b0b22a779fd1b26de08665788","tid":882354,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"只能於指定醫院內處方及服用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068b4c963611430d6f3674928340dbb4f2466f39","tid":882354,"uid":72481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83824e8a09c75bd29a804b0bd4b264781998b629","tid":882354,"uid":3167,"